The '''Lord of White Harbor''' is the ruler of the stronghold and city of [[White Harbor]]. White Harbor is one of the major cities of [[Westeros]], located where the [[White Knife]] river meets [[The Bite|the Bite]]. White Harbor is also the main seaport in [[The North|the North]].

[[House Manderly]] have been the Lords of White Harbor for hundreds of years, holding fealty to [[House Stark]] of [[Winterfell]].
